title: ILinearPatternFeatureData.D1EndSeedReference
description: Gets or sets the pattern seed geometry to offset from the up-to-reference geometry in Direction 1 of this linear pattern feature.
returns: Seed geometry ( vertex , edge , face , or plane ) to offset from ILinearPatternFeatureData::D1EndReference
remarks:
This property is valid only if:
ILinearPatternFeatureData::D1EndUseSeedReference
is set to true
- and -
ILinearPatternFeatureData::D1EndCondition
is set to
swPatternEndCondition_e
.swPatternEndCondition_UpToReference.
